    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Tower of Jank offers:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225940/extras/bc1ebaac05d6772d62106cfd2e1e4a34.poster.avif?t=1771245977\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225940/extras/bc1ebaac05d6772d62106cfd2e1e4a34.webm?t=1771245977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225940/extras/bc1ebaac05d6772d62106cfd2e1e4a34.mp4?t=1771245977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique card combat</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's 2 classes with over 70 cards each. Most of these cards have synergies some of which even I as a developer have not found yet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relics that increase the build variety even further.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Before every run you can take one or more pills that will change how you approach making your build.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play how you want</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use cards by yourself in real time. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can <strong>stop time</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can make it so the <strong>cards are played automatically</strong> and focus on dodging and building the deck.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Difficulty</strong> - the game is hard. You have to break the game or the game breaks you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225940/extras/80f8fd07b5effacc36dc2ec435cfcd05.poster.avif?t=1771245977\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225940/extras/80f8fd07b5effacc36dc2ec435cfcd05.webm?t=1771245977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225940/extras/80f8fd07b5effacc36dc2ec435cfcd05.mp4?t=1771245977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225940/extras/53af2ca42f3a587a7b616b6b9e467114.avif?t=1771245977\" width=609 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
